<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>MAGI Deliberation — {{ record.id }}</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 860px; margin: 2em auto; padding: 0 1em; color: #222; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.4em; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.1em; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: .25em; margin-top: 1.5em; }
    h3 { font-size: 1em; margin: 0 0 .25em 0; }
    blockquote { border-left: 4px solid #555; margin: .5em 0; padding: .5em 1em; background: #f5f5f5; }
    .position { border: 1px solid #bbb; border-radius: 4px; padding: 1em; margin: 1em 0; }
    .mandate { color: #555; font-style: italic; margin: .25em 0; font-size: .9em; }
    .vote { margin: .25em 0; }
    .rationale { white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: .75em; }
    .on-record { font-size: .75em; font-weight: normal; color: #555; margin-left: .5em; border: 1px solid #bbb; border-radius: 3px; padding: .1em .4em; }
    .tally { margin: .5em 0; }
    .crux-box { background: #fff8e1; border-left: 4px solid #e6a817; padding: 1em; margin: 1em 0; }
    .fragile-box { background: #fef3f3; border-left: 4px solid #c0392b; padding: 1em; margin: 1em 0; }
    .citation { color: #666; font-size: .85em; }
    code { background: #eee; padding: .1em .3em; border-radius: 2px; font-size: .9em; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>MAGI Deliberation Record</h1>
<p class="citation">
  Record ID: <code>{{ record.id }}</code> &bull;
  {{ record.created_at }} &bull;
  Tier: {{ record.tier }}
</p>

<h2>Question</h2>
<blockquote>{{ record.question }}</blockquote>

<h2>Outcome: {{ record.outcome }}</h2>
<p class="tally">YES: {{ yes_count }} &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp; NO: {{ no_count }}</p>

{% if record.outcome == 'split' %}
<div class="crux-box">
  <strong>This deliberation could not reach a verdict.</strong>
  The panel is split. The consequence-anchored crux — the question whose resolution
  would most likely change the outcome — is:
  <blockquote>{{ record.crux }}</blockquote>
</div>
{% elif record.outcome == 'fragile_agreement' %}
<div class="fragile-box">
  <strong>Fragile Agreement.</strong>
  The panel reached the same position on incompatible reasons. The shared vote rests
  on rationales that do not reinforce each other. This result is on record as a
  fragile agreement, not as consensus.
</div>
{% endif %}

<h2>Positions</h2>
{% for position, is_minority in positions_with_labels %}
<div class="position">
  <h3>
    {{ position.agent_name }}{% if is_minority %}<span class="on-record">position on record</span>{% endif %}
  </h3>
  <p class="mandate">Mandate: {{ position.agent_mandate }}</p>
  <p class="vote">Vote: <strong>{{ position.vote }}</strong></p>
  <div class="rationale">{{ position.rationale }}</div>
</div>
{% endfor %}

</body>
</html>
